{"tid":1283881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[尋找他爸的故事] 急! 朋友尋親！","createTime":"2019-07-04T03:06:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T03:14:41.000Z","uid":264079,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"45c5bb9be9a0ee0ec016ebe579448078ea10f549","tid":1283881,"uid":264079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:06:11.000Z","msg":"急！有朋友講唔見咗親人！<br />\n<br />\n事源: 自從630後有朋友同我講佢親人唔見咗，以下有最近露面片段:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/2303445459704704/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fvideos%2F2303445459704704%2F&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O4R92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=539c871b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/2303445459704704/</a><br />\n相片:<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8KwyroP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8KwyroP.png&h=1b152457&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如有發現，請大家通知，我朋友心急如焚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似話何耳猿搞多次集會就會尋得到親，希望佢會幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">唔知有無其他人都係咁情況？</span>"},{"pid":"c2299b6bea5e240cb0468b1fe6932913488bb8d4","tid":1283881,"uid":264079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:06:33.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"ae77ef2971148bc5478b50f0d3fe27154f19edf6","tid":1283881,"uid":264079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:06:46.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"f48b992d07c156f6fab4ffe38d0bddbbf0e702e9","tid":1283881,"uid":30273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:06:47.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"2fc30de7e7ca735a545d6ebbf7dec384c5271f2f","tid":1283881,"uid":264079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"